name: AI Beast Mix
description:
AI Beast Mix is probably one of my greatest model merge to achieve semi-realism result for furry character. The model mainly focus on male/ gay furry character but it can also generate female character too. This model seem to be able to support a lot of lora during my testing. However, I don't recommend using this model to train character lora but if train for concept, it might work but I'm not too sure about it.

Unlike my old model Beast Mix, this model have lower chance generate weird/ curse result. Also, Hires.Fix is recommended to get better details and result.

If I'm not mistaken, this model does not use any VAE so don't worry about it. If it does, it's already baked with one of the model during merge process.
